description_html: At the center of the Fiore Stool is its simple, ergonomic seat shell available in both high and low back models. The Fiore barstool can stack 3 high on the floor to create space-saving solutions. Available un-upholstered, with an upholstered seat pad or fully upholstered, Fiore offers various finishes in bright colors and wood veneers to suit any office aesthetic. Truly multifunctional, the Fiore chair enhances any environment while providing a graceful solution for flexible spaces.
